      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DEVIOUS MINDS (7) resumes after four-and-a-half months having ended her juvenile season with a hat-trick of wins, the last two coming from this row. Won the only time she attempted this circuit and distance and should be ready to go off two trial placings. Expecting a bright start to the campaign. ETHANS REVENGE (6) gave a sight when he led and boxed on for a resuming fourth last start, beaten 4 metres at Newcastle. Draws wider but should be improved and didn't miss a place in a four-start maiden campaign, winning twice. BELLAMYS BLAST (5) backs up off a solid fourth in a handy line-up on Monday. Came from this barrier when winning at this circuit and distance prior. Contender. TOLLSA KING (3) last appeared when runner-up here five months ago. Readied with two trials and draws well so keep safe.",
